    "visible_text": "{\"id\":4541,\"date\":\"2020-05-06T08:41:16\",\"date_gmt\":\"2020-05-06T15:41:16\",\"guid\":{\"rendered\":\"https:\\/\\/quantumsf.org\\/?page_id=4541\"},\"modified\":\"2023-09-11T14:18:12\",\"modified_gmt\":\"2023-09-11T21:18:12\",\"slug\":\"videos\",\"status\":\"publish\",\"type\":\"page\",\"link\":\"https:\\/\\/quantumsf.org\\/adult-martial-arts-curriculum\\/videos\\/\",\"title\":{\"rendered\":\"Distance-learning resources\"},\"content\":{\"rendered\":\"\\n<h4 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Adult Program<\\/h4>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p class=\\\"wp-block-paragraph\\\"><em>Forms curriculum<\\/em><\\/p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p class=\\\"wp-block-paragraph\\\">The following forms lessons were filmed during an online Forms Seminar\\u00a0 on May 23, 2020. <\\/p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p class=\\\"wp-block-paragraph\\\">These distance-learning resources were developed during the Shelter-in-Place ordinances of the 2020 Covid-19 pandemic. They don&#8217;t function as replacements to our in-person classes, but remain available for our students who would like to do supplemental martial arts at home. <\\/p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p class=\\\"wp-block-paragraph\\\">To view the written steps to each form, short videos of each form as it is to be performed, and the techniques learned at each rank, please click through the<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/quantumsf.org\\/adult-martial-arts-curriculum\\/\\\" data-type=\\\"URL\\\" data-id=\\\"https:\\/\\/quantumsf.org\\/adult-martial-arts-curriculum\\/\\\"> Adult Curriculum <\\/a>page, choosing the belt your student is *<em>currently<\\/em>* wearing.<\\/p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<p class=\\\"wp-block-paragraph\\\">*<em>Below the forms lessons are a collection of hour-long classes that begin with a 30 minute warmups\\/stretching, and include a 30 minute martial arts lesson. These videos are intended to support students who cannot make it to the regularly-scheduled daily Zoom classes, or would like extra practice.&nbsp;<\\/em><\\/p>\\n\\n\\n\\n<h5 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Basic Form: White Belt<\\/h5>\\n\\n\\n\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\\\">\\n<span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/1mZV81-ph4U?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span>\\n<\\/div><\\/figure>\\n\\n\\n\\n<h5 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Gravity: High White Belt <\\/h5>\\n\\n\\n\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\\\">\\n<span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/7BjZkGH14Nw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span>\\n<\\/div><\\/figure>\\n\\n\\n\\n<h5 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\" id=\\\"block-a55ecb41-eae0-4387-a582-d9295bfbfbcb\\\">Terra Moto: Yellow Belt<\\/h5>\\n\\n\\n\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\\\">\\n<span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/MLHid0GBMYc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span>\\n<\\/div><\\/figure>\\n\\n\\n\\n<h5 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Riverbed: High Yellow Belt<\\/h5>\\n\\n\\n\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\\\">\\n<span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/kB3w9xtLywM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span>\\n<\\/div><\\/figure>\\n\\n\\n\\n<h5 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Attitude: Green Belt<\\/h5>\\n\\n\\n\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\\\">\\n<span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/Uqp21feIbok?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span>\\n<\\/div><\\/figure>\\n\\n\\n\\n<h5 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Waterfall: High Green<\\/h5>\\n\\n\\n\\n<div class=\\\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-8f761849 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\\\" style=\\\"flex-basis:100%\\\">\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\\\">\\n <span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/GgAn3nah7ho?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span>\\n<\\/div><\\/figure>\\n\\n\\n\\n<div class=\\\"wp-block-group\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\\\">\\n<h5 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Spirit: Blue Belt<\\/h5>\\n\\n\\n\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\\\">\\n<span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/KpD-cPNvDI4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span>\\n<\\/div><\\/figure>\\n\\n\\n\\n<h5 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Walk in the Park: High Blue<\\/h5>\\n\\n\\n\\n<figure class=\\\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\\\"><div class=\\\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\\\">\\n<span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/8z2YoGpRtlg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span>\\n<\\/div><\\/figure>\\n<\\/div><\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n\\n\\n<p>While the Quantum San Francisco Dojo physical location has been closed to promote social distancing during the COVID-19 pandemic, we&#8217;ve recorded our Zoom classes and will share a few for the community to practice at home, in the case that you cannot make it to the live classes or would like to take the class again.<\\/p>\\n<p>Lesson Plan: Asterisk Footwork<\\/p>\\n<div id=\\\"v-yr503b52-1\\\" class=\\\"video-player\\\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='768' height='432' src='https:\\/\\/videopress.com\\/embed\\/yr503b52?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\\\"true\\\" allow='clipboard-write'><\\/iframe><script src='https:\\/\\/s0.wp.com\\/wp-content\\/plugins\\/video\\/assets\\/js\\/next\\/videopress-iframe.js'><\\/script><\\/div>\\n<\\/p>\\n<p>Lesson Plan: Basic Footwork<\\/p>\\n<p><span class=\\\"embed-youtube\\\" style=\\\"text-align:center; display: block;\\\"><iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" class=\\\"youtube-player\\\" width=\\\"768\\\" height=\\\"432\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/5uSSu5z5728?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"border:0;\\\" sandbox=\\\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"protected\":false},\"excerpt\":{\"rendered\":\"<p>Adult Program Forms curriculum The following forms lessons were filmed during an online Forms Seminar\\u00a0 on May 23, 2020. These distance-learning resources were developed during the Shelter-in-Place ordinances of the 2020 Covid-19 pandemic. They don&#8217;t function as replacements to our in-person classes, but remain available for our students who would like to do supplemental martial &hellip; <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/quantumsf.org\\/adult-martial-arts-curriculum\\/videos\\/\\\" class=\\\"more-link\\\"><span class=\\\"more-link-text\\\">Read more <span class=\\\"screen-reader-text\\\">Distance-learning resources<\\/span><\\/span><\\/a><\\/p>\\n\",\"protected\":false},\"author\":59510805,\"featured_media\":0,\"parent\":20,\"menu_order\":0,\"comment_status\":\"closed\",\"ping_status\":\"closed\",\"template\":\"\",\"meta\":{\"_coblocks_attr\":\"\",\"_coblocks_dimensions\":\"\",\"_coblocks_responsive_height\":\"\",\"_coblocks_accordion_ie_support\":\"\",\"_crdt_document\":\"\",\"advanced_seo_description\":\"\",\"jetpack_seo_html_title\":\"\",\"jetpa